<paragraph blockId="10.[192,1442,1058,1286]" pageId="10" pageNumber="9">
Eleven specimens were located that matched the locality data given by 
<bibRefCitation author="Gorham HS" box="[1059,1237,1058,1084]" pageId="10" pageNumber="9" pagination="249 - 276" refId="ref8137" refString="Gorham HS. 1884. Supplement. Insecta. Coleoptera. Malacodermata. Lampyridae. Biologia Centrali-Americana 3 (2): 249 - 276." type="journal article" year="1884">Gorham (1884)</bibRefCitation>
. Other specimens were found, but due to label data not matching 
<bibRefCitation author="Gorham HS" box="[740,916,1092,1118]" pageId="10" pageNumber="9" pagination="249 - 276" refId="ref8137" refString="Gorham HS. 1884. Supplement. Insecta. Coleoptera. Malacodermata. Lampyridae. Biologia Centrali-Americana 3 (2): 249 - 276." type="journal article" year="1884">Gorham (1884)</bibRefCitation>
they were excluded from the type series. Two specimens were card-mounted together with a red “type” label. We here designate the specimen on the right as the 
<typeStatus box="[266,371,1159,1185]" pageId="10" pageNumber="9">lectotype</typeStatus>
. The other ten specimens are designated as 
<typeStatus box="[870,1035,1159,1185]" pageId="10" pageNumber="9">paralectotypes</typeStatus>
. Labels for the designated 
<typeStatus box="[1338,1440,1159,1185]" pageId="10" pageNumber="9">lectotype</typeStatus>
specimen are as follows: “SYN-/TYPE” “Type” “V. de 
<collectingRegion box="[812,907,1193,1219]" country="Panama" name="Chiriqui" pageId="10" pageNumber="9">Chiriqui</collectingRegion>
,/ 
<quantity box="[920,1073,1193,1219]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.524" metricValueMax="1.8288" metricValueMin="1.2192" pageId="10" pageNumber="9" unit="ft" value="5000.0" valueMax="6000.0" valueMin="4000.0">4000-6000 ft.</quantity>
/Champion.” “ 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Laporte" authorityYear="1833" box="[1234,1335,1193,1219]" class="Insecta" family="Lampyridae" genus="Photinus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="9" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Photinus</taxonomicName>
/pusillus/ Gorham” “Type.” “B.C.A.Col.III.(2)/ 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Laporte" authorityYear="1833" box="[589,694,1226,1253]" class="Insecta" family="Lampyridae" genus="Photinus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="9" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Photinus</taxonomicName>
/pusillus,/Gorham”. A red label is added with the following text: “ 
<typeStatus box="[201,359,1260,1286]" pageId="10" pageNumber="9">LECTOTYPE</typeStatus>
/ 
<taxonomicName authority="Gorham" authorityName="Gorham" authorityYear="1884" box="[367,652,1260,1286]" class="Insecta" family="Lampyridae" genus="Photinus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="9" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pusillus">
<emphasis box="[367,553,1260,1286]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="9">Photinus pusillus</emphasis>
Gorham
</taxonomicName>
/Designated by/Martin and Saxton 2020”
</paragraph>
